dct_title_s: Neōtatos politikos chartēs Hellados / Vivliopōleion S. Kontou & D. Phylaktou
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights and gradient tints. Depth shown by bathymetric tints. "Ekdoseis bibliopoleiou S. Kontou & D. Phylaktou" [Publications of bookstore of S. Kontos & D. Phylaktos]. Εκδόσεις βιβλιοπωλείου Σ. Κοντού & Δ. Φυλακτού. On verso: Primary economic productions by region shown pictorially. Both maps include ancillary map of Cyprus (1:1,700,000) and ancillary map of Rhodes with locator map of Rhodes with reference to Turkey. Recto includes locator map of Greek in Europe. Title translation: New political map of Greece. Verso: Geophysical and (economic) production map of Greece. With (on verso): "Geōphysikos & paragōgikos chartēs Hellados" at scale 1:1,000,000. Γεωφυσικός & παραγωγικός χάρτης Ελλάδος.
dct_publisher_sm: Athēnai : Vivliopōleion S. Kontou & D. Phylakto, [1969?].
